<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>rssCloud v2: Please Notify</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>rssCloud v2: Please Notify</h1>
    <p>Posting to /pleaseNotify is your way of alerting the server that you want to receive notifications when one or more resources are updated.</p>

    <form method="POST" action="pleaseNotify">
        <label for="domain">Domain</label>
        <input type="text" id="domain" name="domain" placeholder="example.com">

        <label for="port">Port</label>
        <input type="text" id="port" name="port" placeholder="80" required>

        <label for="path">Path</label>
        <input type="text" id="path" name="path" placeholder="/notify" required>

        <label for="registerProcedure">Register Procedure</label>
        <input type="text" id="registerProcedure" name="registerProcedure" placeholder="weblogUpdates">

        <label for="protocol">Protocol</label>
        <input type="text" id="protocol" name="protocol" placeholder="http-post" required>

        <label for="url1">Resource URL</label>
        <input type="text" id="url1" name="url1" placeholder="https://example.com/feed.rss" required>

        <button type="submit">Please Notify</button>
    </form>

    <p class="mt-20">
        <a href="/">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    </p>
</body>
</html>
